Build the AgentOS runtime without EdgeJS's second-engine compatibility path.

The AgentOS target runs inside the existing V8 isolate and uses the owned
POSIX spawn surface. It must neither configure QuickJS's Wasmer backend nor
compile the Edge safe-mode launcher. Also correct the simdjson source-relative
include used by the CLI.

